hopobject.body: Could you ask him to call me? ursodeoxycholic acid medscape Every year, almost 27,000 graduating middle-school students take the entrance exam for the nine high schools: Stuyvesant, Bronx Science, Brooklyn Tech, Staten Island Tech, Brooklyn Latin, High School of American Studies at Lehman College, Queens High School for the Sciences at York College and High School for Mathematics, Science and Engineering at City College. Just over 5,200 were offered spots last year.
